---
import ServiceLayout from '../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---
<ServiceLayout
    title="Web Design & Development – Super Sonic"
    description="Strategic, conversion-focused websites engineered for clarity, speed, and long-term growth."
    canonicalUrl="https://supersonic.media/web-design/"
>
    <section class="service-hero">
        <div class="tag">Web Design &amp; Development</div>
        <h1>Websites built to <span class="gold">perform.</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">Strategic, conversion-focused websites engineered for clarity, speed, and long-term growth.</p>
        <div class="hero-line"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="overview">
        <div class="overview-inner">
            <div class="overview-text">
                <div class="overview-label">Overview</div>
                <p>A website is more than a digital brochure. It&#8217;s your first impression, your positioning statement, and your primary conversion tool.</p>
                <p>We design and develop custom websites that align brand, structure, and performance into one cohesive system.</p>
                <p><strong>This isn&#8217;t decoration. It&#8217;s design with intent.</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="overview-principles">
                <div class="principle reveal">
                    <h4>Who you&#8217;re targeting</h4>
                    <p>Every design decision starts with understanding the audience and their expectations.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle reveal">
                    <h4>What action you want them to take</h4>
                    <p>Clear conversion paths reduce friction and drive measurable results.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="principle reveal">
                    <h4>How the experience reduces friction</h4>
                    <p>Remove barriers between intent and action at every touchpoint.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="deliver">
        <div class="section-tag">What We Deliver</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Strategy, design, and development &mdash; under one roof.</h2>
        <div class="deliver-grid">
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M22 12h-4M6 12H2M12 6V2M12 22v-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Strategy &amp; Structure</h3>
                <p>We define positioning, user flow, and conversion logic before design begins.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Messaging hierarchy</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Page architecture</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Conversion mapping</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Call-to-action strategy</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20a7 7 0 003.9-1.2L12 15l-3.9 3.8A7 7 0 0012 20z"/><path d="M12 15l3.9-3.8A7 7 0 0012 2a7 7 0 00-3.9 9.2L12 15z"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Design</h3>
                <p>Clean, modern interfaces built for clarity and confidence.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Custom UI design</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Responsive layouts</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Design systems</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Brand alignment</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="deliver-card reveal">
                <div class="deliver-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg></div>
                <h3>Development</h3>
                <p>High-performance builds with scalability in mind.</p>
                <div class="deliver-items"><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Custom development</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Performance optimization</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>SEO-ready structure</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Analytics integration</span></div><div class="deliver-item"><span class="deliver-bullet"></span><span>Clean, maintainable code</span></div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="performance">
        <div class="perf-header">
            <div class="section-tag">Built for Performance</div>
            <h2>Built with intent.</h2>
            <p>We don&#8217;t launch and disappear. Every site is engineered to compound results over time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="perf-grid">
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#9889;</div><h3>Speed</h3><p>Optimized load times that reduce bounce and improve conversion.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128241;</div><h3>Mobile</h3><p>Responsive performance across every device and screen size.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128269;</div><h3>SEO Structure</h3><p>Clean markup, structured data, and crawlable architecture.</p></div>
            <div class="perf-item reveal"><div class="perf-icon">&#128202;</div><h3>Tracking</h3><p>Conversion tracking and analytics from day one.</p></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ideal">
        <div class="ideal-inner">
            <div class="section-tag">Ideal For</div>
            <h2>Is this the right fit?</h2>
            <div class="ideal-items">
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Businesses ready to elevate their positioning</span></div>
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Companies investing in serious growth</span></div>
                <div class="ideal-item reveal"><span class="ideal-arrow">&#8594;</span><span>Teams who want long-term infrastructure, not templates</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="service-cta">
        <div class="cta-bg"></div>
        <h2>Ready to build a website that <span class="gold">actually works?</span></h2>
        <p class="cta-sub">Tell us what you&#8217;re building. We&#8217;ll show you what&#8217;s possible.</p>
        <div class="cta-btn-wrap">
            <a href="/start/" class="btn-primary">Start a Project <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 13L13 3M13 3H5M13 3v8" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
        </div>
    </section>
</ServiceLayout>
